<br>
Ya can generally AE anywhere where mobs dont have too many HPs for their level, the stuff can be chain stuned, and the stuff doesnt have too high resists.  Id recommend not doing it in the hole, cus lotta stuff resists good, things have lotta hp, and I think some of the mobs are flaged as giants so they cant be stunned.  CoM is great.  Karnors is great.  Ive never done it in seb,but i heard ya can do it there in some rooms.   <p><table border="0" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1">
